p.vn:
saying,
‘We played the flute for you and you did not dance;
we sang a lament and you did not mourn.’

in order that what was spoken through the prophet would be fulfilled, who said,
“I will open my mouth in parables;
I will proclaim what has been hidden since the creation.”A quotation from Ps 78:2Some manuscripts have “since the creation of the world”
